{
  "stem": "27507.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now, he wasn't there at that moment, so they left a paper with his wife and asked that he should appear there next day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And when she asked if he has to take anything, like warm clothes or something, they said, no.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's just a short-- we'll have a brief interview and that's going to be over in an hour's time or maybe a bit less.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he will come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There is absolutely nothing to worry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which means the Russian secret police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they arrested him because-- they arrested him, obviously, because he was the local factory owner.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because of that, he was an hostile element.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was later sent to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was in a gulag, in a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he died there or was killed during the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we didn't find it out except late-- except after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And his wife, of course, never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When he didn't reappear, of course we were-- immediately we understood that something is wrong.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And since my father had the same name, Stok, and they-- when the [INAUDIBLE] came, asked for Mr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Stok, so it was lucky that my father was not there, because they would have arrested him instead probably.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we thought it would be-- we can't stay any more in the villa and who moved out of the villa, and rented for a while a room elsewhere in Rowne.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we moved out of Rowne all together and we started wandering for weeks in eastern Poland, in Wolyn, moved by peasants' carts, usually, or going-- going with a peasant cart and a horse somewhere in very muddy roads.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was raining, because it was already late September or October.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we moved from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
